A top Isibaya actress has been arrested in connection with the attempted murder of her husband and murder of his bodyguard and is expected to appear in the Pretoria magistrate's court on  Wednesday. Police arrested the woman on  Tuesday after evidence allegedly linked her to the shooting incident on January 28, according to Gauteng police spokesperson Capt Kay Makhubele. "The 29-year old female suspect was arrested on suspicion of being involved in the attempted murder of her husband and murder of the husband's bodyguard." This is a developing story.